response.overview: October 18th, 2009 :: Eight tag teams are divided and the partners are placed on separate Cibernetico squads! Mike Quackenbush, Hallowicked, Player Uno, Matt Jackson, Carpenter Ant, Lince Dorado, Cheech, and Soldier Ant face off against Fire Ant, Jigsaw, Nick Jackson, Player Dos, Cloudy, Frightmare, Green Ant, and Helios! In an all-rudo cheatfest for the ages, Ultramantis Black, Chuck Taylor, and STIGMA fight Crossbones, Icarus, and Colin Delaney! Matches featured:  1. Los Ice Creams vs The Throwbacks  2. Vin Gerard vs Ryuichi Kawakami  3. Daizee Haze & Bullfight Sora vs Sara Del Rey & La Malcriada  4. Sal Rinauro vs Claudio Castagnoli  5. Icarus, Crossbones & Colin Delaney vs STIGMA, Chuck Taylor & UltraMantis Black  6. The Roughnecks vs Osirian Portal  7. Torneo Cibernetico Match Mike Quackenbush, Lince Dorado, Player Uno, Soldier Ant, Carpenter Ant, Matt Jackson, Hallowicked & Cheech vs Jigsaw, Fire Ant, Nick Jackson, Player Dos, Cloudy, Frightmare, Green Ant & Helios
response.title: Chikara Cibernetico Increible
